nodes.text: Dashh was a bounty hunter and commentator on Gundark's Gear Datalog during the early years of the New Republic. Dashh once used a T-289 gas grenade on a Wookiee; while the grenade eventually worked, the Wookiee's temper allowed him to get some hits in on Dashh. The bounty hunter spent a month receiving bacta treatments that cost more than the bounty.
